ROBERGE v. WINNE et al., (two cases.) (Supreme Court, General Term, Second Department. December 1, 1893.) Action by Franklin P. Roberge against Maria N. Winne and another.

Argued before BARNARD, P. J., and DYKMAN and PRATT, JJ.

No opinion. Submissions withdrawn. See 24 N. Y. Supp. 562.
